import React, {useState} from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import { useHistory } from "react-router-dom"; // components export default function CardSettings() { const AddDetails = () => { const[criminal_name,setCriminal_name]=useState("") const[criminal_age,setCriminal_age]=useState("") const[criminal_image,setCriminal_image]=useState(null) const[status,setStatus]=useState("") const[crime_committed,setCrime_committed]=useState("") const history = useHistory() const AddCriminalDetail = async () => { let formField=new FormData() formField.append('criminal_name', criminal_name) formField.append('criminal_age', criminal_age) if(criminal_image!=null){ formField.append('criminal_name', criminal_name) } formField.append('Status', status) formField.append('crime_committed', crime_committed) } } return ( <>
CRIMINAL DATA
Criminal Details
setCriminal_name(e.target.value)} />
setCriminal_age(e.target.value)} />
setCriminal_image(e.target.files[0])} />
OTHER DETAILS
setStatus(e.target.value)} />
setCrime_committed(e.target.value)} />
); }
